### Doctor-Patient Management System API Tests
### REST Client Extension (VS Code)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

---
### 1. Register a new Patient
# @name registerPatient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rahul Sharma",
  "email": "rahul.sharma88@testmail.com",
  "phone": "9812345670",
  "dob": "1988-05-15",
  "password": "RahulSecretPassword@2026"
}

---
### 1.5 Register a new Hospital and Admin
# @name registerHospital
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register-hospital
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "adminName": "Global Health Admin",
  "email": "admin@globalhealth.com",
  "password": "GlobalAdminPassword!1",
  "hospitalName": "Global Health Hospital",
  "address": "789 Global Boulevard",
  "phone": "9998887770"
}

---
### 2. Login as Patient
# @name loginPatient
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "rahul.sharma88@testmail.com",
  "password": "RahulSecretPassword@2026"
}

@patientToken = {{loginPatient.response.body.token}}

---
### 3. Get Patient Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 4. Login Admin (Newly Registered Admin)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@globalhealth.com",
  "password": "GlobalAdminPassword!1"
}

@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

---
### 5. Create a Doctor (Admin)
### Note: This doctor will be automatically attached to this Admin's active Hospital!
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dr. Anil Desai",
  "email": "anil.desai@globalhealth.com",
  "specialty": "Neurology",
  "qualifications": "MBBS, MD Neurology",
  "experience": 12,
  "fees": 1200,
  "clinic": "Global Health Neurological",
  "gender": "Male"
}

---
### 6. Toggle Doctor Active Status (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/doctors/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}

---
### 7. View Platform Doctors (Public - No Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/doctors

---
### 8. Search Doctors (Patient)
### Note: This now includes the strict Hospital name and address in the response!
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/doctors?specialty=Neurology
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 9. Get Specific Doctor Profile (Patient)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/doctors/1
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 10. Admin Analytics (Admin - Scoped)
### Note: Admins can only see stats relating to THEIR hospital!
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---
### 11. Doctor Login (Use temp password returned in Step 5)
# @name loginDoctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "anil.desai@globalhealth.com",
  "password": "TEMP_PASSWORD_FROM_STEP_5"
}

@doctorToken = {{loginDoctor.response.body.token}}

---
### 12. Doctor Changes Password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/password
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "TEMP_PASSWORD_FROM_STEP_5",
  "newPassword": "DoctorSecure@456"
}

---
### 13. Doctor Creates Slot
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-04-02T00:00:00.000Z",
  "startTime": "2026-04-02T11:00:00.000Z",
  "endTime": "2026-04-02T11:30:00.000Z"
}

---
### 14. Doctor Views Slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/slots
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

---
### 15. Doctor Deletes Slot
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/slots/2
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

---
### 16. Admin Views Doctors (Scoped)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---
### 17. Admin Views Patients (Scoped)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}} giving [] although it has patients in db

---
### 18. Admin Views Appointments (Scoped)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admins/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---
### 19. Patient Books Appointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slotId": 2,
  "clientTime": "2026-04-02T11:00:00.000Z"
}

---
### 20. Patient Appointment History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 21. Patient Cancels Appointment
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/appointments/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

---
### 22. Doctor Views Appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

---
### 23. Doctor Updates Appointment Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/doctors/appointments/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}